des:
Do you want some wicked laughs after a day at work? Or maybe a compliment to start your day? A standup comedy while doing your chores? Or a twisted joke to start a party?

You can stop looking because Adult Humor got you covered!

Just start by saying, "Alexa, open Adult Humor", to unlock a whole new world of fun.

Disclaimers:
- Jokes and comedies may contains mature language and may not be appropriate for all ages.
- We DO NOT own any rights to the media contents. All comedies are streamed directly from public and official Youtube channels.
